WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.769
Lately, the Lord said, 'Brandon, I need you to encourage my people.

00:00:03.769 --> 00:00:15.000
I need you to tell them about what's coming: about the glory, about the last outpouring, the Holy Ghost, miracle restoration, and revival.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.844
' I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:17.129 --> 00:00:19.464
I have another video for you, of course.

00:00:19.809 --> 00:00:26.946
I told you all it's like looking at a thin quarter or whatever you have in your country—a coin.

00:00:26.946 --> 00:00:31.936
You can either focus on the dark or you can focus on the light.

00:00:31.936 --> 00:00:43.285
It's like two sides of a coin: the darkness is going to get darker in these last days with the birthing pains, but the Lord told me the light is going to start getting lighter.

00:00:44.039 --> 00:00:47.079
You can see it; it'll be tangible.

00:00:47.079 --> 00:00:53.069
The last outpouring, a great harvest of souls, is what's about to happen.

00:00:53.069 --> 00:01:17.871
We're about to see one of the greatest things, like Bible times, like when Moses parted the Red Sea and walked across dry land, the plagues, and all the things you know—seeing blinded eyes open, deaf ears pop open, and autistic children completely delivered and set free by the power of God.

00:01:17.871 --> 00:01:20.024
We're about to see those things.

00:01:21.119 --> 00:01:27.006
If the Bible were still being written today, we would be part of the next chapter.

00:01:27.006 --> 00:01:33.050
I truly believe it with all my heart; that's how amazing these miracles are going to be.

00:01:33.050 --> 00:01:39.000
I believe with all my heart that people will be translating from one place to another, going and preaching the gospel.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:45.720
You may be in a city in America and all of a sudden you're in Africa, Asia, Australia, or South America.

00:01:51.588 --> 00:01:56.948
I believe those are the kinds of things we're going to start to see—the glory of God.

00:01:58.034 --> 00:02:19.379
These testimonies that I'm about to show you, that Sister Billye here—she read off a bunch of prophecies that Brother Hagin gave from the '80s and the '70s and right before he went home, about the last outpouring, about the glorious church rising up and being what we were called to be.

00:02:19.949 --> 00:02:31.364
This one was given in 1980: 'We're right on the verge of the greatest move and manifestation of the spirit of God this world has ever seen.

00:02:31.364 --> 00:02:33.076
Praise God, here we go.

00:02:33.076 --> 00:02:53.336
' And if you'll give the more earnest heed unto these things which you have heard—so think about, this was back in 1980 about faith and healing—but those things which you've heard about the Holy Spirit, about angels, about divine visitations, about visions and dreams.

00:02:53.336 --> 00:03:01.293
'And upon my handmaidens I'll pour out my spirit and they'll prophesy; my young men will prophesy, the young women will prophesy.

00:03:01.293 --> 00:03:10.058
' The anointing and the outflow of the spirit of God shall be great and amazing in these days, and there shall be visitations of angels.

00:03:10.396 --> 00:03:15.480
He goes on to speak about the glory of the Lord and the cloud of glory.

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:16.130
Praise God!

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:22.400
Gloria likes this part so much; it's one of her favorite prophecies from Brother Hagin.

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:29.200
'You will flow in the supernatural as your mind will be changed.

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:30.080
' Praise God!

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:35.148
I renew mine now; I didn't catch that part before, Gloria.

00:03:35.148 --> 00:03:51.395
'Your heart shall be prepared and your mind will be changed until you will flow in the supernatural as naturally as a bird flies in the air.

00:03:51.395 --> 00:03:59.159
You will flow in the supernatural as naturally as a fish will swim in water.

00:03:59.554 --> 00:04:06.439
You will flow in the supernatural as naturally as you breathe the very air.

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:06.829
' Praise God!

00:04:06.829 --> 00:04:16.340
'You will not be conscious of your faith; you'll not be conscious of what's going on around you, but rather you'll be more conscious of the flow of the spirit of God.

00:04:16.685 --> 00:04:21.595
He will manifest himself and he will accomplish that which he desires for you.

00:04:21.595 --> 00:04:26.209
See, these are the last days and this is the end time.

00:04:26.209 --> 00:04:27.355
' Thank you, Jesus!

00:04:27.355 --> 00:04:32.554
'And you shall walk, and you shall run, and you shall fly.

00:04:32.554 --> 00:04:38.880
' Praise God, literally and spiritually speaking!

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:39.240
Hallelujah!

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:50.220
I chose some other ones because I want you to see this one given in 2002.

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:54.969
The Lord told us what to do to get it.

00:04:54.969 --> 00:05:07.279
'We are just about to enter into an area in the realm of the spirit in which only a few of us have touched, but it will be widespread.

00:05:07.279 --> 00:05:09.346
' Thank you, Jesus!

00:05:09.346 --> 00:05:18.268
'And all whose hearts are open, and whose minds are clear, and who are sincere and honest—those are the ones that will move in.

00:05:26.994 --> 00:05:33.405
For a great cloud of glory is hanging just over our heads.

00:05:33.405 --> 00:05:34.424
' Praise God!

00:05:34.424 --> 00:05:42.224
'And that cloud will burst into a torrent of outflow of the rain of the spirit.

00:05:42.224 --> 00:05:45.040
' That's what you saw, Lucy.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:53.817
'And the power of God shall not only be in us but rest upon us, and the plan and the purpose of God shall be consummated.

00:05:53.817 --> 00:05:54.949
' God has a plan!

00:05:57.769 --> 00:06:06.171
Not only for your life and mine, not only for your church and my ministry, but God has a plan for the last days.

00:06:06.171 --> 00:06:09.840
Be honest, sincere, and determined.

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:20.430
'I'm walking and will walk in his plan and fulfill his purpose, for these are the last days.

00:06:20.430 --> 00:06:23.840
' It's time for us to change our thinking in some areas.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:30.800
It's time for us to listen to our hearts and listen to our spirits for counsel.

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:31.745
'I need counseling!

00:06:31.745 --> 00:06:33.004
Can you counsel me?

00:06:33.004 --> 00:06:38.341
' You have a counselor on the inside of you, the Holy Spirit, and he will counsel with you.

00:06:38.341 --> 00:06:41.279
He will talk to you; he will talk with you.

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:45.390
He will instruct you; he will show you just what to do, and you'll be glad.

00:06:45.390 --> 00:06:49.405
And the plan of God will be consummated and the end shall come.

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:59.764
The dead in Christ shall rise, and we which are alive and remain will be caught up together to meet the Lord in the air, and so shall we ever be with the Lord.

00:06:59.764 --> 00:07:01.440
So rejoice and be glad!

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:02.080
Praise God!

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:18.048
Now, this one: 'There will be a revival of the supernatural—not only the supernatural in casting out devils, not only the supernatural in healing the sick, not only the supernatural in speaking with other tongues, but the supernatural in the seen realm.

00:07:19.502 --> 00:07:22.457
Men will see the glory of God.

00:07:22.457 --> 00:07:28.350
A cloud will hang over certain congregations, even the church buildings, for days at a time.

00:07:28.350 --> 00:07:36.720
' And everybody who passes by—sinner and saint alike—will say, 'What in the world is that?

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:38.811
I've never seen anything like that!

00:07:38.811 --> 00:07:45.560
' And there will be in other places the fire of the spirit that will actually become literal.

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:54.659
In the spirit realm, some of us have seen it; we've been conscious of the fire of God, but the fire will actually come into manifestation.

00:07:54.999 --> 00:08:00.656
There will be people, sinners as well as saints, that will see fire over the heads of the people.

00:08:00.994 --> 00:08:10.151
There will be people driving down the street or down the highway and they'll see fire on the tops of the buildings, and they will come and say, 'What does all this mean?

00:08:10.151 --> 00:08:20.559
' But you see—now get this—the Lord will use signs of his presence to bring people in in the last days.

00:08:20.799 --> 00:08:23.897
That's how we're going to get the harvest right there.

00:08:23.897 --> 00:08:27.408
The outpouring of the spirit is going to draw them in.

00:08:27.408 --> 00:08:33.599
'I will use signs of his to bring people in in the last days.

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:34.589
' Praise the Lord!

00:08:34.589 --> 00:08:43.026
Men and women too will be transported like Philip was and found in another place.

00:08:43.026 --> 00:08:51.070
And great shall be the reward thereof, for the Lord God is the same today as he was yesterday.

00:08:51.070 --> 00:08:54.818
His power has not diminished and his name is still the same today.

00:08:54.818 --> 00:09:05.089
He can make the iron ax head float today; he can divide the river just for two men to cross over today; he can feed five thousand with a little boy's lunch.

00:09:05.089 --> 00:09:08.839
He is the miracle-working God!

00:09:08.839 --> 00:09:11.805
Yes, this is what I've been looking for lately: the instruction.

00:09:11.805 --> 00:09:12.822
What do we do?

00:09:14.439 --> 00:09:17.440
Listen: 'Brag on him.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:19.480
' Praise the Lord!

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:30.778
Brag on him, lift him up, draw attention unto him, tell about how great he is.

00:09:30.778 --> 00:09:32.867
How awesome is our God!

00:09:32.867 --> 00:09:40.702
Lord, do that tonight: get up in faith and tell what great things he's going to do.

00:09:40.702 --> 00:09:45.535
He's going to do it, and we're going to see it!

00:09:45.535 --> 00:09:46.000
Hallelujah!

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:50.240
'For the purpose of it all is that you may be fishers of men.

00:09:51.085 --> 00:09:58.460
Quit fishing in your own bathtubs; there are not any fish in your own bathtub!

00:09:58.810 --> 00:10:06.169
Go out where the fish are and throw out the nets—not the hook, the nets—and pull them in!

00:10:06.169 --> 00:10:06.564
' Hallelujah!

00:10:06.564 --> 00:10:16.710
And bring them in, and the glory of the Lord shall shine, and the end time shall come, and he's going in the Holy Ghost.

00:10:16.710 --> 00:10:30.103
He's been praying in the Holy Ghost, and he begins to say this: 'Moving into that place is fueled by prayer.

00:10:30.103 --> 00:10:37.755
It's fueled by prayer, fired by the Spirit, and ignited with His glory.

00:10:37.755 --> 00:10:39.014
' Wow, say that again.

00:10:39.014 --> 00:10:43.160
He got so tickled over saying that he started saying, 'Hallelujah to Jesus, glory to God.

00:10:43.160 --> 00:10:45.172
' I said, 'Glory to God, glory to God, hallelujah.

00:10:45.172 --> 00:10:46.172
' Fueled by prayer.

00:10:46.172 --> 00:10:50.988
And he starts talking about it; he said, 'If there's no fuel, there's nothing to ignite.

00:10:50.988 --> 00:10:53.048
' He said, 'Notice what the Spirit said.

00:10:53.048 --> 00:11:04.822
' I never thought of it—it came out of the inside of me—he said, 'I never thought of it before: fueled by prayer, fired by the Spirit, and ignited with His glory.

00:11:04.822 --> 00:11:07.519
' We have to stop and analyze that.

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:14.529
Then he comes to this: 'If there is no fuel, there's nothing to fire.

00:11:14.529 --> 00:11:19.507
If there's no fuel, there's nothing to fire.

00:11:19.507 --> 00:11:27.051
It is fueled by prayer.

00:11:27.051 --> 00:11:30.760
' We've got a big key here: prayer.

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:40.840
All this praying in the Spirit, the Holy Ghost said, is going to be fueled by prayer.

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:52.500
There will be churches in the body of Christ, in buildings where they meet, where the glory of God will fill the place like a cloud and everybody will see it.

00:11:52.910 --> 00:12:04.714
And when that glory comes in manifestation, people walking by and driving by in their cars, even the unsaved, will feel the power; and folks down at the end of the block will fall under the power in their homes.

00:12:04.714 --> 00:12:05.468
Thank You, Father.

00:12:05.468 --> 00:12:10.720
And they will wonder, 'What is this strange power that's in manifestation for the glory of God?

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:25.216
' And the power of God will, like a cloud, hang over whole cities because you prayed—because you believed.

00:12:42.785 --> 00:12:43.130
I just want to do a recap here.

00:12:43.130 --> 00:12:44.854
So, here we are.

00:12:44.854 --> 00:12:59.280
She's talking about how we're going to fuel this end-time revival, how we get the manifestation of what we're believing for instead of just waiting for it to happen.

00:13:06.937 --> 00:13:12.000
I know it's in God's timing, but just like Brother Hagin was talking about it, prayer is a major key to this, interceding for the last outpouring.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:34.920
Just like it was—you know, if we go back to what John Kilpatrick said with the Pensacola Revival—they had prayer there every night for a while, and they prayed for two years for a revival to break out in that area.

00:13:41.507 --> 00:13:42.320
And so it was birthed through intercessory prayer, continually praying in the Spirit.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:53.429
That church prayed and prayed, and then on a Father's Day, the manifestation of the outpouring started to manifest and took place.

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:13.555
It came.

00:14:13.555 --> 00:14:24.520
At its very start, there were three men: George Whitefield, John Wesley, and Charles Wesley—three Englishmen—and they formed a club called The Holy Club.

00:14:40.004 --> 00:14:40.639
In their Holy Club, they endeavored to live a holy life and to pray.

00:14:40.639 --> 00:14:45.519
Their Holy Club had an unusual thing that happened to it.

00:14:45.519 --> 00:14:51.149
I shall read you about it right here.

00:14:51.149 --> 00:14:54.749
I wonder what book that is.

00:14:54.749 --> 00:15:02.139
It had grown to 32 members when there came—just think about that right there.

00:15:02.139 --> 00:15:07.227
Sorry to interrupt again, but 32 people praying, that's all.

00:15:07.227 --> 00:15:16.274
Whenever I do a prayer thing on here, we'll have 3,500 people pray in the Spirit for at least 15 minutes.

00:15:16.274 --> 00:15:20.976
So just think about that; we have great power and unity in prayer.

00:15:20.976 --> 00:15:23.433
So, thirty-some people here.

00:15:23.433 --> 00:15:29.900
Upon them, a great outpouring of the Spirit on New Year's Day, 1739.

00:15:29.900 --> 00:15:36.319
Over 60 people were present at that moment when the Wesleys, George Whitefield, and others received God's power in the Spirit.

00:15:36.319 --> 00:15:44.160
Waves of unspeakable joy passed over them, and they prostrated themselves on the ground in awe and adoration.

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:46.448
Thank God.

00:15:46.448 --> 00:16:03.535
It gave these men a deep conviction that He was about to do something great and wonderful in England.

00:16:14.500 --> 00:16:14.840
And as this great revival moved, it brought them to America.

00:16:14.840 --> 00:16:17.145
It moved in the English-speaking world.

00:16:17.145 --> 00:16:21.784
There are chapters in here—Paul Brady, where are you?

00:16:21.784 --> 00:16:32.109
—about how it moved to Ulster and how it moved to Belfast and the things that happened.

00:16:32.109 --> 00:16:38.656
But in the United States of America, it became known as the Great Awakening.

00:16:58.759 --> 00:16:59.028
It was from 1739 until 1791.

00:16:59.028 --> 00:17:03.813
There was a great connection between the Great Awakening and the American Revolution.

00:17:03.813 --> 00:17:09.159
The outcome of the Great Awakening was the United States of America.

00:17:10.640 --> 00:17:19.440
And one of the leaders—and these things are all in this book right here—was greatly affected by a man named Finney.

00:17:27.342 --> 00:17:27.605
The Finney revivals.

00:17:29.205 --> 00:17:38.100
And there's so much clue in here as to what happened with Finney, and I want to read you just a little bit of it.

00:17:39.020 --> 00:17:40.200
Bless the Lord, hallelujah.

00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:42.000
Revival fires follow Finney.

00:17:47.290 --> 00:17:52.697
His biographer said that perhaps the most remarkable account of the manifestations of the Holy Spirit's power since apostolic days was in Finney's meetings.

00:17:52.697 --> 00:17:58.640
It is crowded with accounts of spiritual outpourings which remind one of the Day of Pentecost.

00:18:16.046 --> 00:18:16.400
The intensity and constancy of his ardor were surprising.

00:18:19.039 --> 00:18:19.644
The sacred fire never seemed to burn low.

00:18:19.644 --> 00:18:32.186
His campaign, which began in New York State, was absolutely preparing the way for the mighty move of revival that swept America in 1857 and 1858.

00:18:32.186 --> 00:18:43.500
More than a million people came into the kingdom of God under his ministry, and though the population was not so large, 85% of the professed converts in the Finney revivals remained true to God.

00:18:43.500 --> 00:18:48.586
These revivals spread and blessed churches from city to city and around and across America.

00:18:48.586 --> 00:19:01.515
God poured—in the early days of his walk with the Lord, Finney learned about prevailing prayer and prayer burdens, and he would spend time in prayer, often going to the woods to be alone with God.

00:19:13.806 --> 00:19:14.234
God poured out a spirit of prayer upon other people who followed Finney and went with him.

00:19:14.234 --> 00:19:17.325
Much private prayer accompanied this revival.

00:19:21.834 --> 00:19:22.126
And so Finney began to preach.

00:19:22.126 --> 00:19:25.960
He went to a town in New York named Antwerp.

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:32.571
He walked through the streets, he heard profanity, and he spent the rest of the day in prayer.

00:19:35.244 --> 00:19:36.644
And before a few days, most of its 2,250 citizens were converted.

00:19:36.644 --> 00:19:37.186
Wow.

00:19:37.186 --> 00:19:38.960
He visited a nearby village.

00:19:51.469 --> 00:19:51.720
In the first service, the schoolhouse was full.

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:54.519
After 15 minutes, the congregation began to fall from their seats.

00:19:54.519 --> 00:19:58.080
They fell in every direction and cried for mercy.

00:19:58.080 --> 00:20:06.467
'If I had had a sword in each hand, I could not have cut them all from their seats as fast as they fell,' he wrote.

00:20:06.467 --> 00:20:10.200
Indeed, nearly the whole congregation were either on their knees or prostrate.

00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:19.493
'I think in less than two minutes from the first shock that fell upon them, everyone prayed for himself who was able to pray at all.

00:20:19.493 --> 00:20:25.840
I, of course, was obliged to stop preaching, for no one any longer paid attention to me.

00:20:25.840 --> 00:20:28.525
' Do it again, do it again, Lord.

00:20:31.187 --> 00:20:33.531
The meetings went on and on, and whole towns would get saved.

00:20:35.253 --> 00:20:35.946
He went to New York, Oneida County.

00:20:35.946 --> 00:20:38.590
God gave a prayer burden on Friday.

00:20:38.590 --> 00:20:41.076
Sunday, God came in power at the church services.

00:20:41.076 --> 00:20:44.240
Finney prevailed in prayer and spoke in several parts of the town.

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:45.800
A Mrs.

00:20:45.800 --> 00:20:49.320
Harris had wrestled in prayer night and day.

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:52.571
When she met Finney, she said, 'The Lord has come.

00:20:52.571 --> 00:20:55.926
This work will spread over all this region.

00:21:03.034 --> 00:21:03.320
A cloud of mercy overhangs us, and we shall see a great work of grace that has never yet been seen.

00:21:03.320 --> 00:21:06.799
' Finney said that Mrs.

00:21:06.799 --> 00:21:12.080
Harris's face had a most unearthly, heavenly glow that was plainly from Heaven.

00:21:12.080 --> 00:21:14.480
She had won a revival through prayer.

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:16.445
Praise God, through prayer.

00:21:31.804 --> 00:21:38.217
And then after the revival fire burned in the West for a while, it came to the town of Rome.

00:21:40.394 --> 00:21:45.320
God gripped the people with such Holy Spirit conviction, Finney was afraid that the people could not control their emotions.

00:21:45.320 --> 00:21:56.354
Finney led in prayer at the close of the meeting in a low, unemotional voice, trying to restrain the people who had begun to weep and sigh.

00:21:58.879 --> 00:22:01.193
He urged them to control their feelings and go home without speaking a word to anyone.

00:22:05.335 --> 00:22:09.834
The people obeyed, but their sighing and sobbing continued as they went down the street to their homes.

00:22:09.834 --> 00:22:12.620
At daybreak, the people began sending for Finney.

00:22:14.973 --> 00:22:17.903
He spent the morning going from house to house to pray with the people.

00:22:25.279 --> 00:22:26.304
He finally announced a meeting for inquirers, and many more were convicted in the evening service.

00:22:26.304 --> 00:22:34.170
People were so overwhelmed by the Holy Spirit's conviction that he dismissed the service and asked the people to go home.

00:22:34.170 --> 00:22:43.640
Revival went on for twenty nights with a prayer meeting once a day, a meeting for inquirers at another time, and ministers' meetings at night.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:47.907
Some people collapsed from conviction in the church services and some later in their own homes.

00:22:47.907 --> 00:22:56.365
It had become common across America that people, by and large, in great groups of cities, were not born again.

00:23:09.006 --> 00:23:09.354
He would go into these places and these things would happen.

00:23:09.354 --> 00:23:15.360
Three men spent a day drinking and condemning the revival until one of them fell down dead.

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:23.520
Nearly all of the adult population of Rome, New York, was brought to Christ—lawyers, merchants, physicians, and town leaders.

00:23:24.659 --> 00:23:30.166
The ministers said, "So far as my congregation is concerned, the Millennium has come.

00:23:30.166 --> 00:23:34.980
" Everyone who came into the village felt an overwhelming sense of God's presence.

00:23:43.177 --> 00:23:43.491
The sheriff of Utica, New York, twenty miles away, came on business.

00:23:45.777 --> 00:23:50.413
He had laughed and mocked at the reports of the revival.

00:23:50.413 --> 00:23:58.099
As his sleigh crossed the canal one mile outside of Rome, an awesome feeling of the presence of God gripped him.

00:24:00.397 --> 00:24:09.600
The nearer to the village he came, the more powerfully he sensed God's presence.

00:24:28.025 --> 00:24:28.360
The sheriff found the people in the business establishments too overcome with the awe of God—so overcome they could hardly speak without trying to keep from weeping.

00:24:40.491 --> 00:24:40.937
The sheriff got up several times and went to the window.

00:24:40.937 --> 00:24:46.028
He hurried to complete his business and hastened back to Utica.

00:24:46.028 --> 00:24:47.979
Soon he was converted.

00:24:47.979 --> 00:24:51.920
Bless the Lord, Finney urged the people to pray to God earnestly.

00:24:51.920 --> 00:25:07.000
